      "span_text": "We have confirmed the outstanding performance of this system for small RNA isolation from both plasma and cerebrospinal fluid.  With the goal of determining whether low RNA recovery or the presence of PCR inhibitors in our initial isolations could have contributed to largely negative results, we repeated the above experiments after isolating RNA with the Exiqon Biofluids procedure from previously unthawed macaque plasma."
